sections.heading: and safety regulations; violations; penalty
sections.text: Every person who shall violate any of the provisions of sections 48-401 to 48-423 shall be guilty of a Class II misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1919, c. 190, tit. IV, art. IV, § 20, p. 562;C.S.1922, § 7701;C.S.1929, § 48-420;R.S.1943, § 48-424;Laws 1965, c. 284, §
